      "section": "AI \u2014 News & Analysis",
      "source": "Simon Willison",
      "title": "SQLite Query Result Formatter Demo",
      "url": "https://simonwillison.net/2026/Apr/11/sqlite-qrf/#atom-everything",
      "published": "2026-04-11T19:35:31+00:00",
      "summary": "Tool: SQLite Query Result Formatter Demo\n    See my notes on SQLite 3.53.0. This playground provides a UI for trying out the various rendering options for SQL result tables from the new Query Result Formatter library, compiled to WebAssembly.\n    \n        Tags: tools, sqlite"
    },
